- Master!
- Excuse me.

1830
01:24:27,620 --> 01:24:29,050
What brings you here!

1831
01:24:29,620 --> 01:24:31,520
What brings you here?

1832
01:24:32,250 --> 01:24:33,660
What brings you here!

1833
01:24:33,960 --> 01:24:35,590
- I heard...
- What brings you here?

1834
